thesis and determine whether `aiops-k8s-08` and its CPU usage rate exhaustion are impacting CartService and Redis performance. Let's examine the evidence:\n\n### Trace Data Analysis:\n1. **Key Latency Observations**:\n   - **CheckoutService to CartService (aiops-k8s-08)**:\n     - Operation `POST /hipstershop.CartService/EmptyCart` shows extreme latency compared to normal averages (15.24× higher than normal), indicating significant contention.\n   - **CartService operations hosted on node `aiops-k8s-08`**:\n     - `HGET` on Redis experiencing super elevated latency (7932.39ms vs 1553.15ms, ~5.11× normal) directly tied to node `aiops-k8s-08`.\n\n2. **Error Observations**:\n   - While the logs showed issues with AdService, trace data shows predominant latency and degraded performance affecting CartService and Redis related to node `aiops-k8s-08`.\n\n### Conclusion:\nGiven the substantial delays and performance degradation correlated with CartService operations hosted on aiops-k8s-08, along with the metric data pointing to CPU constraints, the hypothesis that aiops-k8s-08 causes resource contention resulting in performance impact holds significant merit. \n\nTherefore, the stance is \"SUPPORT\".\n\n### JSON Output\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\"latency_spike\", \"checkoutservice->cartservice\", \"cartservice->redis\", \"aiops-k8s-08\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-08\",\n      \"reason\": \"Resource exhaustion impacting operations on CartService and Redis, evidenced by high latency multipliers.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Latencies for CartService operations on node aiops-k8s-08 escalated to ~15.24× (EmptyCart) and ~5.11× (HGET on Redis); node CPU usage also spiked.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```", "metric_analysis_findings": "根据上下文以及我的分析总结，我同意该状态中提出的结论。以下是结合提供的所有证据后，对于假设的支持情况的更新说明。\n\n### 分析确认:\n1. **节点资源异常 (aiops-k8s-08)**:\n   - `node_cpu_usage_rate` 在 `aiops-k8s-08` 节点上急剧上升，从正常的 22.44% 飙涨到 42.08%。\n   -